message.text:
📣CALLING ALL ASPIRING ITHM VOCALISTS & INSTRUMENTALISTS! ⏩

Are you ready to take your talent to the next level?

 Join the ITHM MUSIC MAKERS this September 16-17 and be part of something powerful, passionate, and purpose-driven.

📍 𝘃𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲: Alfredo Reyes Hall (ARH) 204 
📅𝗦𝗰𝗵𝗲𝗱𝘂𝗹𝗲:

SEPTEMBER 15 | MONDAY | 3:00 PM - 5:00 PM
SEPTEMBER 17 | WEDNESDAY | 9:00 AM - 11:00 AM

Pre-register through this link to choose your audition and interview schedule:
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdedzbaeqHy8nQeF0UgLFuXLv5ODeD0m2lDRFuiCRyGPRBvlw/viewform?usp=header

For instrumentalists, submit your online auditions here: 
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSci_vttPiZpsmBt9KbBK1A4LsUXkiLjqFgaiyF0VLXd2uWiZA/viewform?usp=header

 Bring your sound. Bring your heart. Let’s make More than Music — let’s make an impact.  ⏩

#ITHMMusicMakers #MoreThanMusicMM #AuditionCall #SeptemberSound
#GandaGalingTalinoatTalento
